<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_422" id="210v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_422_r1l19">Dem Edeln <expan>vvolgep<ex>orn</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Grafen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l20">cʒu Seẏn vnd <expan>Öberſt<ex>er</ex></expan> Truchſes in Brabant </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l21"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr nu nechſt hie beẏ . vns cʒu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> vvart </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l22">vnd vvir mit <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> redten von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Cʒolfreẏu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l23">ın <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu Brabant / <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
                        Jr ew gen vns gnediglich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l24">erputt / darcʒu vns die
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvol geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        vvie Jr ew gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l25">Jn auch <expan>gnedıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>erpot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / des alles vvir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l26"><expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ
                                <expan>dinſtl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> ewr
                        gnad mıt <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l27">daʒ Jr ew die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in
                                <expan>ſolıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo ſie cʒu ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l28"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> auch fürbaſʒ
                                <expan>gnedıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beuolhen ſein laſſen vvollet /
                        Als vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l29"><expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        getrawen cʒu ew <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd das vmb ewr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l30">cʒu <expan>allencʒeıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vvıllıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> vvöllen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan>
<expan><ex>ter</ex>ʒ<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">a</hi></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l31"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Mathie
                                <expan>ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan>
<expan>A<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xij<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_422" id="210v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem edeln, <expan>wolgep<ex>orn</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>, grafen czu Seyn und
                                <expan>öberst<ex>er</ex></expan> truchses in Brabant</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir nu nechst hie bey uns czu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> wart und wir mit
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> redten von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>czolfreyu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wegen in <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> czu Brabant, <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
                        ir ew gen uns gnediglich erputt, darczu uns die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wol gesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        wie ir ew gen in auch <expan>gnedigl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>erpot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, des alles wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                                <expan>dinstl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> ewr
                        gnad mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir ew die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>solich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>, wo sie czu ew <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        auch fürbasz <expan>gnedigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> bevolhen sein lassen wollet,
                        als wir <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>en</ex></expan> getrawen czu ew
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und das umb ewr gnade czu
                                <expan>allenczeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>willigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> wöllen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> <expan><ex>ter</ex>z<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">a</hi></expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Mathie <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>
<expan>a<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
